('Mammuthus primigenius', 'Woolly Mammoth', '猛犸象', 'Pleistocene Megafauna', -4000, '~4,000年前', '欧亚、北美', '[Pleistocene Megafauna] Woolly Mammoth (Mammuthus primigenius). Historic range: 欧亚、北美. 冻尸DNA丰富、耳结构/吼声/心率完美适合音乐层', '', FALSE, 'No historic pharmaceutical use. De-extinction and aDNA research may yield insights into cold-adaptation proteins and comparative immunogenomics; any medical application remains speculative and ethically contested.', '人类狩猎+气候变化. (狩猎→hunting; 人类→human activity; 气候→climate change)', '人类狩猎+气候变化', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mammuthus_primigenius', 10, 9, 'high', 'Sketchfab "Woolly Mammoth"', '冻尸DNA丰富、耳结构/吼声/心率完美适合音乐层'),
('Mammuthus columbi', 'Columbian Mammoth', '哥伦比亚猛犸象', 'Pleistocene Megafauna', -10000, '~10,000年前', '北美', '[Pleistocene Megafauna] Columbian Mammoth (Mammuthus columbi). Historic range: 北美. 骨骼/迁徙路径数据', '', FALSE, 'No historic pharmaceutical use. De-extinction and aDNA research may yield insights into cold-adaptation proteins and comparative immunogenomics; any medical application remains speculative and ethically contested.', '人类+气候. (人类→human activity; 气候→climate change)', '人类+气候', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mammuthus_columbi', 9, 8, 'high', 'Sketchfab "Columbian Mammoth"', '骨骼/迁徙路径数据'),
